response.original_title: M&RPA Movie 3: The Rise of Eggman & Cell: Triathlon Of Allies
response.overview: M&RPA Movie 3: The Rise of Eggman & Cell: Triathlon Of Allies is a full feature length film recap of season 3 of the critically acclaimed "Mordecai & Rigby: Plush Adventures" series on YouTube. Uploaded Jul 1, 2024 by Toaster Swag Studios.  This third installment of the critically acclaimed M&RPA series on YouTube dot com. Movie 3 details the chronicles of the cast form "Regular Show" interacting with various pop-culture characters.
response.tagline: Critically acclaimed series brought together to form one. awesome. movie.
